789
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:19,600
Not to meals or birthdays

790
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,160
or relationships.

791
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:24,640
Just because this is your present

792
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:26,000
doesn't mean
it has to be your future.

793
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:28,200
Who knows?
Maybe someday you can

794
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:30,120
get out of here
without having to escape.

795
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:34,360
Yeah, and aren't you glad
you didn't shut down today?

796
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,480
Well, this cake is pretty good.

797
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:42,040
Come on. Come on.
Who doesn't want to see

798
00:32:42,120 --> 00:32:43,680
a Ray Palmer love letter?

799
00:32:43,760 --> 00:32:45,400
You have to open it.
